    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Dim, greenish light spreads within a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on you. The light spreads around corners, and it lasts until the jutsu ends.<br />When a creature moves into the jutsu's area for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there, that creature must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take 4d10 Necrotic damage, and it gains one rank of exhaustion, taking half as much damage on a success. Any levels of exhaustion caused by this jutsu go away when the jutsu ends.</p>",
